short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: the internet is full of you

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: See yourself reflected in cyberspace as every web page rearranges itself to reveal your underlying and overwhelming presence on the internet. Your participation perpetuates and sustains our connected network. The internet is full of you and only you.
